dct_title_s: Geographers' six inch map of Central London
dct_description_sm: Geographers' Map Co., Ltd. Shows postal districts and borough boundaries. Attached booklet of Index to streets and postal districts is missing. In lower margin: "This Map is based upon the Ordnance Survey Map with the sanction of the Controller of H. M. Stationery Office.".
